These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, mirinda, hot-chocolate, water, tea
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, bus, roller, trike, van
 1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 4. the person driving the van is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
 5. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
 6. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person drinking tea##7
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 8. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
10. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
11. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
14. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person drinking mirinda##7
15. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
16. the person drinking water is not the person driving the roller##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate | lemonade | iced-tea | water | tea | mirinda |
| Transport   | scooter | bus    | motorbike  | trike  | roller            | van  |

