.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
House: tower, townhouse, farmhouse, modern, ranch-style, gothic-revival
There 6 different types of food: cabbage, radish, grapes, kiwi, apple, cucumber
 1. the modern house is not the person eating cucumber##6
 2. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4
 3. the person eating apple is not to the right of the person eating kiwi##8
 4. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person eating cucumber is between the modern house and the person eating radish##2
 6. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
 7. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
 8. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
 9. the townhouse house is not the person eating kiwi##6
10. the tower house is on the far left or far right##3
11. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the person eating grapes##8
12. the person eating cucumber is not to the right of the ranch-style house##8
13. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the tower house##3
14. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person eating radish##1
15. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| House   | farmhouse | gothic-revival | townhouse | ranch-style | modern | tower |
| Food     | grapes  | cabbage  | radish         | cucumber | apple    | kiwi   |

