.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, game, alhambra, siglo, dannemann, bongani
The people have 6 different hobbies: magic-tricks, board-games, fishing, rock-climbing, dancing, chess
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
 2. the game-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the game-smoker##8
 5. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 6. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
 8. the siglo-smoker is not to the right of the siglo-smoker##8
 9. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the dannemann-smoker and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
13. the bongani-smoker is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is chess##2
14. the game-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
15. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the swisher-smoker##7
16. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
17. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
18. the dannemann-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
19. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the swisher-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
| Cigar   | dannemann   | alhambra | bongani    | siglo      | game | swisher |
| Hobby         | board-games | dancing  | magic-tricks | chess | fishing   | rock-climbing  |

