.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: march, june, july, october, january, april
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, coffee, sprite, water, juice
 1. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
 2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person drinking 7up##7
 6. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person drinking water is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 9. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
10. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
11. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person who's birthday is in april##7
13. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
14. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
15. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
16. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
17. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| Birthday    | march | april    | january     | october  | june    | july |
| Beverage   | 7up  | water | hot-chocolate | juice | coffee | sprite     |

