.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-7::.
6 different pets are kept: rat, goat, pony, ferret, hamster, lizard
6 different games are played: chess, canasta, whist, scrabble, billiard, go
 1. the owner of the lizard is not to the right of the person playing go##8
 2. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
 3. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the goat and the person playing go##2
 4. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 5. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
 6. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 8. the person playing go is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
 9. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person playing billiard is between the owner of the rat and the person playing scrabble##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |     6      |
| Pet   | pony    | rat | lizard    | goat | ferret   | hamster |
| Game         | chess | canasta  | billiard | scrabble   | whist | go |

