 1. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person who's sport is handball##6
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 4. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the person drinking juice##7
 5. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking 7up##2
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
 9. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
10. the person who's sport is climbing is not the person drinking coffee##6
11. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
13. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Beverage   | juice | cola | 7up  | sprite     | almond-milk | coffee |
| Sport           | cricket        | parkour    | badminton | biathlon | climbing     | handball  |

